title.narrative: Caribbean Criminal Assets Recovery Team Payments and Allowances

description.narrative: This activity (Caribbean Criminal Assets Recovery Team Payments and Allowances) is a component of Caribbean Criminal Assets Recovery Programme reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £1,106,024. This component benefits West Indies, regional, and works in the following sector(s): Anti-corruption organisations and institutions, Security system management and reform. , with the following implementing partners: Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office. The start date is 01-10-2012 and the end date is 01-02-2016.
